      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LOCHINVAR GRACE (7) led throughout to score two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 7 length 5th at this track (23.40). Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from four starts. Has ability and looks hard to stop. ZIPPING DELORIS (8) is racing well without winning, recording three minors on end, the latest hitting the ground running with a fast early sectional but finishing in the minors again when third (23.16) over 400m at this track. Yet to miss the placings in five runs from this box, including two wins. Well placed and gets her chance. SHANGHAI SPY (2) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by a nose at this track in a handy 23.59 beating Daniel Keeping. Boasts a strong record from this draw with four wins and two minor placings from 10 starts. Has definite claims. FASCINATE GLORY (1) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.",
